Yes — we can start with **A** now, and pivot to **B (Claude)** later if you want. Below is a complete, **state-of-the-art single-page static site** (HTML + CSS) you can deploy immediately. No WordPress. No plugins. No JS required.

I am not going to slow you down with questions. This will render cleanly with placeholder images, and you can swap in your real assets as you go.

---

## Folder structure (recommended)

```
catalyst-static/
  index.html
  styles.css
  assets/
    logo.svg
    hero.jpg
    initiative-1.jpg
    initiative-2.jpg
    initiative-3.jpg
    favicon.png
```

---

## Create files via Terminal (per your preference)

Run this from anywhere:

```bash
mkdir -p ~/Documents/catalyst-static/assets
cd ~/Documents/catalyst-static
touch index.html styles.css
ls -la ~/Documents/catalyst-static ~/Documents/catalyst-static/assets
```

Verification command (confirms correct paths + files):

```bash
find ~/Documents/catalyst-static -maxdepth 2 -type f -print
```

---

## 1) `styles.css`

Paste this entire file into `~/Documents/catalyst-static/styles.css`:

```css
/* Catalyst Static Site
   Fonts: Georgia (headings), Montserrat (body)
   Colors: Navy #121531, Cyan #42A4D9, Text #0A0C1D, Light #F7F9FC
*/

:root{
  --navy:#121531;
  --cyan:#42A4D9;
  --text:#0A0C1D;
  --light:#F7F9FC;
  --white:#FFFFFF;

  --radius:14px;
  --radius-sm:10px;

  --shadow-sm: 0 10px 30px rgba(18,21,49,.10);
  --shadow-md: 0 18px 60px rgba(18,21,49,.16);

  --container: 1200px;
  --gutter: clamp(18px, 4vw, 40px);

  --h1: clamp(2.2rem, 3.2vw, 3.1rem);
  --h2: clamp(1.65rem, 2.1vw, 2.15rem);
  --h3: clamp(1.15rem, 1.2vw, 1.35rem);
  --p:  clamp(1.02rem, 0.9vw, 1.1rem);

  --lh: 1.55;
}

*{ box-sizing:border-box; }
html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; }
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family: "Montserrat", system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  color:var(--text);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--light), #fff 35%, #fff 100%);
  line-height: var(--lh);
}

img{ max-width:100%; height:auto; display:block; }
a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }

.container{
  max-width: var(--container);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
}

.skip-link{
  position:absolute;
  left:-9999px;
  top:auto;
  width:1px;height:1px;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.skip-link:focus{
  left: var(--gutter);
  top: 18px;
  width:auto;height:auto;
  padding:10px 12px;
  background:var(--white);
  border:1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.2);
  border-radius:10px;
  z-index:9999;
}

/* Header */
.site-header{
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 1000;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.75);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.08);
}
.header-inner{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  gap:18px;
  padding: 14px 0;
}

.brand{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:12px;
  min-width: 220px;
}
.brand-mark{
  width: 42px; height: 42px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, var(--cyan), var(--navy));
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}
.brand-name{
  display:flex; flex-direction:column;
}
.brand-name strong{
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  letter-spacing: .2px;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--navy);
}
.brand-name span{
  font-size:.86rem;
  color: rgba(10,12,29,.70);
}

/* Nav */
.nav{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap: 18px;
}
.nav a{
  font-size: .95rem;
  color: rgba(10,12,29,.82);
  padding:10px 10px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}
.nav a:hover{
  color: var(--navy);
  background: rgba(66,164,217,.10);
}

.header-cta{
  display:flex;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items:center;
}

/* Buttons */
.btn{
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: .95rem;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: transform .12s ease, box-shadow .12s ease, background .12s ease, border-color .12s ease, color .12s ease;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn:active{ transform: translateY(1px); }
.btn-primary{
  background: var(--cyan);
  color: var(--white);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(66,164,217,.30);
}
.btn-primary:hover{
  box-shadow: 0 14px 44px rgba(66,164,217,.40);
}
.btn-secondary{
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--navy);
  border-color: rgba(18,21,49,.22);
}
.btn-secondary:hover{
  border-color: rgba(66,164,217,.80);
  background: rgba(66,164,217,.10);
}
.btn-invert{
  background: var(--white);
  color: var(--navy);
}
.btn-invert:hover{
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
}

.pill{
  display:inline-flex;
  gap:10px;
  align-items:center;
  padding: 8px 12px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: .86rem;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.16);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.22);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
}

/* Hero */
.hero{
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  padding: clamp(54px, 6vw, 92px) 0 clamp(38px, 5vw, 72px);
  color: var(--white);
  background:
    linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(18,21,49,.92), rgba(18,21,49,.70)),
    url("./assets/hero.jpg") center/cover no-repeat;
}
.hero::after{
  content:"";
  position:absolute;
  inset:-40%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 65% 25%, rgba(66,164,217,.45), transparent 55%);
  transform: rotate(-12deg);
  pointer-events:none;
}
.hero-inner{
  position:relative;
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.15fr .85fr;
  gap: clamp(18px, 4vw, 56px);
  align-items: center;
}
.hero h1{
  margin: 10px 0 14px;
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  font-size: var(--h1);
  line-height: 1.12;
  letter-spacing: .15px;
}
.hero p{
  margin: 0 0 20px;
  font-size: clamp(1.02rem, 1.05vw, 1.15rem);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.90);
  max-width: 58ch;
}
.hero-actions{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 18px;
}
.hero-card{
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}
.hero-card h3{
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}
.metrics{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 14px;
}
.metric{
  padding: 12px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
}
.metric strong{
  display:block;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}
.metric span{
  display:block;
  margin-top: 4px;
  font-size: .86rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.86);
}

/* Sections */
.section{
  padding: clamp(48px, 6vw, 86px) 0;
}
.section h2{
  margin: 0 0 12px;
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  font-size: var(--h2);
  color: var(--navy);
  letter-spacing: .15px;
}
.section .lead{
  margin: 0 0 26px;
  font-size: var(--p);
  color: rgba(10,12,29,.78);
  max-width: 70ch;
}

.grid{
  display:grid;
  gap: 18px;
}
.grid-4{ grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
.grid-3{ grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }

.card{
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.08);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 18px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}
.card h3{
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  font-size: var(--h3);
  color: var(--navy);
}
.card p{
  margin: 0;
  color: rgba(10,12,29,.80);
  font-size: 0.98rem;
}
.card:hover{
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  transition: transform .12s ease, box-shadow .12s ease;
}

.icon-badge{
  width: 40px; height: 40px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(66,164,217,.14);
  border: 1px solid rgba(66,164,217,.25);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.icon-badge svg{ width: 20px; height: 20px; fill: var(--cyan); }

/* Initiatives */
.initiative{
  padding: 0;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.initiative .thumb{
  width:100%;
  aspect-ratio: 16/9;
  background: #e8eef7;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.08);
}
.initiative .thumb img{
  width:100%;
  height:100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}
.initiative .body{
  padding: 16px 18px 18px;
}
.tags{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 12px;
}
.tag{
  font-size: .82rem;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(18,21,49,.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.10);
  color: rgba(18,21,49,.80);
}

/* Insights */
.post-meta{
  margin-top: 10px;
  font-size: .86rem;
  color: rgba(10,12,29,.62);
}

/* CTA band */
.cta{
  background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--navy), #0d1030 55%);
  color: var(--white);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.08);
}
.cta-inner{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  align-items:flex-start;
  gap: 16px;
}
.cta h2{ color: var(--white); }
.cta p{
  margin:0;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.88);
  max-width: 78ch;
}
.cta-actions{
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap: 12px;
}

/* Footer */
.footer{
  padding: 34px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.08);
  background: #fff;
}
.footer-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 18px;
  align-items:start;
}
.footer a{ color: rgba(10,12,29,.78); }
.footer a:hover{ color: var(--navy); }
.small{
  font-size: .9rem;
  color: rgba(10,12,29,.70);
}
.footer-bottom{
  margin-top: 18px;
  padding-top: 18px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(18,21,49,.08);
  display:flex;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 980px){
  .hero-inner{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .grid-4{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .grid-3{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .footer-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .brand{ min-width: 0; }
}
@media (max-width: 640px){
  .nav{ display:none; } /* simplest possible; can add a minimal mobile menu later */
  .grid-4{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .grid-3{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .metrics{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .footer-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
```

